{"tid":196602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"踩港撚要打擊所有想反抗既人","createTime":"2017-04-11T12:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T08:08:01.000Z","uid":10937,"like":24,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"336dc7ba3ce4521a2bff2d799ad6c3520dec9ee4","tid":196602,"uid":10937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:07:29.000Z","msg":"睇穿晒你地啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當中有幾多打手又有幾多真心膠附和係你地先知！<br />\n<br />\n乜支那賊匪已經唔請五毛而轉請打手對付連登，成本又貴左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n班仆街講到香港人幾咁廢幾咁冇用，講到香港已經無力回天<br />\n<br />\n就係要消滅大家既幻想同希望，向班走唔到既人洗腦，要&quot;認命&quot;，唔再諗點樣翻身，做個服從支那共匪既順民<br />\n<br />\n希望連登仔清醒d，唔好中計<br />\n<br />\nps唔好再重複你地之前既論調，咩講事實，咩玻璃心，好悶啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2846fa1f90ceb6c6c27a1e1d27e0904a62a7e68b","tid":196602,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:11:29.000Z","msg":"不嬲都覺得班踩港撚係五毛"},{"pid":"3f709a5c2442b76ac08435f638766962eb79c747","tid":196602,"uid":10937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:14:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不嬲都覺得班踩港撚係五毛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個d唔知係高級五毛定打手識捉連登仔心理，唔似高登個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fc0f53c1972516efa94c772fd998c7ac0cbbf2","tid":196602,"uid":10937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:16:24.000Z","msg":"冇踩港撚入黎推post就證實班人係打手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />