<br />\n<br />\n同埋，打手唔知包唔包括你呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不服來辯，幫我推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n辯乜鬼，你都玩到歸邊，講句唔啱聽就係敵人，支那人劣根性出哂黎<br />\n<br />\n至於香港人抵唔抵死，而家仲係咁on99，有人幫佢地做義士仲走去笑人，佢地唔抵死咩？<br />\n<br />\n仲有，唔好一碌鳩打一船人，你歸做「踩港」嗰班，有啲係想香港好，有啲係心灰意冷，當然亦有五毛，五毛好易認，日日講支付寶點好點好嗰啲，亦有啲怨毒痴線佬，唔理三七廿一乜都屌一餐，同你差唔多。"},{"pid":"3c0384f5848a71df2875e130fc7f4d5438b615fa","tid":196602,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:17:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>踩得有道理都算5毛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">後生仔</span>要聽下人意見<br />\n唔好下下咁自大<br />\n最緊要知錯能改</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仆街死老坑就彈開啦，香港嘅未來唔係你呢d死老坑架，咪撚阻住香港進步啦，你以為踩香港人，香港人就要認輸認命？返支那食屎啦你！"},{"pid":"e85885c69cf9787a23c0784e4a8c8885435d49a4","tid":196602,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:18:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>踩得有道理都算5毛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後生仔要聽下人意見<br />\n唔好下下咁自大<br />\n最緊要知錯能改</blockquote><br />\n真係講道路嘅，指出香港人有乜問題就ok, 但有班人係要下下拉埋中國嚟講"},{"pid":"a1ec1f86c5e9433e61ca1178561b97ce1667dacc","tid":196602,"uid":353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:19:15.000Z","msg":"香港LUMBA WAN!"},{"pid":"62d2f8542b78ce33537b7397d497fafbe3a8ff6f","tid":196602,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:21:18.000Z","msg":"都要有野俾位人踩先得㗎<br />\n事實係香港都好撚多仆街"},{"pid":"9e906324bf6fa9cc09406d1617f591c66e9fdb0e","tid":196602,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:25:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><block